gobblin.compaction.mapreduce.avro

Class MRCompactorAvroKeyDedupJobRunner

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.compaction.mapreduce.MRCompactorJobRunner
      • gobblin.compaction.mapreduce.avro.MRCompactorAvroKeyDedupJobRunner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<MRCompactorJobRunner>, Runnable

    public class MRCompactorAvroKeyDedupJobRunner
extends MRCompactorJobRunner
    A subclass of MRCompactorJobRunner that configures and runs MR compaction job for Avro data. To dedup using entire records set compaction.use.all.attributes=true. Otherwise, a schema needs to be provided by compaction.avro.key.schema.loc, based on which the dedup is performed.
